snippet.title: Hack RUN Mini Walkthrough (levels 1 to 5)
snippet.description:
This walkthrough will show you how to get to level 5. Keep using the 'help' command on each system to reach higher levels. If you get stuck, you can always use the 'tips' command to view helpful Hints & Answers to each of the puzzles. 

Thanks for watching and thanks for playing Hack RUN!
